
<h4>About the contests</h4>

<p>RPGDX occasionally organizes contests. Participating in our contests you'll generally perform the following steps.</p>

<ol>
<li>Make sure you have an account on RPGDX and that you're logged in.</li>
<li>Add a (new) project to RPGDX.</li>
<li>Go to the contest page to subscribe with the project.</li>
</ol>

<p>Specific rules for a contest and participation info can be found on each contest page.</p>
